Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.course

Class Activity

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.course.Activity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Conflict
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Course
    public abstract class Activity
extends java.lang.Object
implements Conflict
    Activity contains information useful for appearing on a schedule, such as title and meeting days and times. Activity is the abstract super class to Event and Course, providing the abstract getShortDisplayArray(), getLongDisplayArray(), and isDuplicate(Activity) methods
    Author:
    Ethan Taylor
